@N2453:  fetch the next character in the string
@N2454:  actually draw the character!
@N2455:  prepare for next char in loop
@N2460:  test for a negative number as the marker for the string end; branch out if done
@N2466:  pointer to the next character to display
@N2471:  segments should be lit for each symbol.
